## Authorization Letter  


Subject: Authorization for Leachain International Corp. Ltd. to Use KLAPP Cosmetics Brand Logo  


We, KLAPP Cosmetics GmbH, hereby authorize Leachain International Corp. Ltd., located in Taiwan, to use our official brand logo for marketing, promotional, and commercial purposes across all online and offline platforms within Taiwan. This authorization strictly excludes the territories of China, Hong Kong, and Macau.  


Furthermore, Leachain International Corp. Ltd. is also authorized to address and take appropriate actions against any unauthorized use of the KLAPP Cosmetics brand logo on any platform within Taiwan.  


This authorization remains valid until revoked in writing by KLAPP Cosmetics GmbH.  


